<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Alerts & Notifications</title>

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #eef8fb;
      color: #123;
    }

    header {
      height: 64px;
      background: #ffffff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 32px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #cbd5dc;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 50px;
      height: 60px;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .brand h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #155e75;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 32px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #5b6b7a;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    nav .active {
      background: #155e75;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 22px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .user {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .avatar {
      background: #155e75;
      color: white;
      padding: 9px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .notification-btn {
      position: relative;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: #e6f7fc;
      border: 1px solid #a7dce8;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 9px 11px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .notification-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: -6px;
      right: -6px;
      background: #dc2626;
      color: white;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .page {
      padding: 32px 40px;
    }

    .page-title {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .page-title h2 {
      font-size: 30px;
      color: #155e75;
    }

    .back-link {
      text-decoration: none;
      background: #155e75;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .summary-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .summary-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #c5d4db;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 22px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(21,94,117,0.08);
    }

    .summary-card small {
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #6b7f89;
    }

    .summary-card strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: #155e75;
    }

    .alerts-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .alerts-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #c5d4db;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .alerts-header {
      background: #e6f7fc;
      padding: 18px 24px;
      color: #155e75;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .alert-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 90px 1fr 130px;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5edf1;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .alert-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .severity {
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-align: center;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .critical {
      background: #fee2e2;
      color: #dc2626;
    }

    .warning {
      background: #fff4d6;
      color: #b7791f;
    }

    .info {
      background: #d8f0f4;
      color: #155e75;
    }

    .resolved {
      background: #e8f5e9;
      color: #2e7d32;
    }

    .alert-content h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      color: #123;
    }

    .alert-content p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #5b6b7a;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .alert-meta {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #7a95a1;
    }

    .side-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #c5d4db;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 22px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(21,94,117,0.08);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .side-card h3 {
      color: #155e75;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .building-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .building-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 13px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5edf1;
    }

.building-row strong {
  background: #fff4d6;
  color: #b7791f;

  padding: 4px 10px;

  border-radius: 20px;

  font-size: 11px;

  font-weight: 800;
}

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px;
      color: #7a95a1;
      font-size: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #cbd5dc;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <div class="brand">
    <img src="gemeinde_wappen.png" alt="Gemeinde Sonnenfeld" class="logo">
    <div>
      <h1>Gemeinde Sonnenfeld</h1>
      <small>Energy Monitoring System</small>
    </div>
  </div>

  <nav>
    <a href="index.html">Dashboard</a>
    <a href="#">Buildings</a>
    <a href="#">Reports</a>
    <a href="#">Settings</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="user">
    <a href="notifications.html" class="notification-btn">
      🔔
    
    </a>
    <span class="avatar">EM</span>
    <span>Energy Manager</span>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="page">

  <div class="page-title">
    <h2>Alerts & Notifications</h2>
    <a href="index.html" class="back-link">← Back to Dashboard</a>
  </div>

  <section class="summary-grid">
    <div class="summary-card">
      <small>Critical Alerts</small>
      <strong>2</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="summary-card">
      <small>Warnings</small>
      <strong>3</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="summary-card">
      <small>Resolved Today</small>
      <strong>1</strong>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alerts-layout">

    <div class="alerts-card">
      <div class="alerts-header">Current Warnings</div>

      <div class="alert-item">
    
        <span class="severity critical">Critical</span>
        <div class="alert-content">
          <h3>High water consumption</h3>
          <p>Regionalspital Sonnenfeld exceeded the water threshold by 18%.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="alert-meta">
          Today<br>
          09:15 CET
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="alert-item">
        <span class="severity critical">Critical</span>
        <div class="alert-content">
          <h3>Electricity threshold exceeded</h3>
          <p>Sekundarschule Sonnenfeld used 12% more electricity than expected.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="alert-meta">
          Today<br>
          08:40 CET
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="alert-item">
        <span class="severity warning">Warning</span>
        <div class="alert-content">
          <h3>Water consumption increased</h3>
          <p>Sekundarschule Sonnenfeld shows a water consumption increase of 2 %.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="alert-meta">
          Yesterday<br>
          16:40 CET
        </div>
      </div>



      <div class="alert-item">
        <span class="severity warning">Warning</span>
        <div class="alert-content">
          <h3>Gas consumption increased</h3>
          <p>Sporthalle Zentrum shows a gas consumption increase of 1.4%.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="alert-meta">
          Yesterday<br>
          16:40 CET
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="alert-item">
        <span class="severity warning">Warning</span>
        <div class="alert-content">
          <h3>Sensor connection unstable</h3>
          <p>Kindergarten Bergblick sent incomplete meter data.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="alert-meta">
          Yesterday<br>
          11:20 CET
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="alert-item">
        <span class="severity info">Info</span>
        <div class="alert-content">
          <h3>Monthly report ready</h3>
          <p>The energy report for January 2025 was generated successfully.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="alert-meta">
          2 days ago<br>
          14:05 CET
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="alert-item">
        <span class="severity resolved">Resolved</span>
        <div class="alert-content">
          <h3>Solar data synchronized</h3>
          <p>Solar production data from Schwimmbad Sonnenfeld is now available.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="alert-meta">
          Today<br>
          07:30 CET
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside>
<div class="side-card">
  <h3>Buildings Requiring Attention</h3>

  <div class="building-list">

    <div class="building-row">
      <span>Sekundarschule Sonnenfeld</span>
      <strong>2 Alerts</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="building-row">
      <span>Regionalspital Sonnenfeld</span>
      <strong>1 Alert</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="building-row">
      <span>Sporthalle Zentrum</span>
      <strong>1 Alert</strong>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

      <div class="side-card">
        <h3>Alert Categories</h3>

        <div class="building-list">
          <div class="building-row">
            <span>Water</span>
            <strong>2</strong>
          </div>

          <div class="building-row">
            <span>Electricity</span>
            <strong>1</strong>
          </div>

          <div class="building-row">
            <span>Gas</span>
            <strong>1</strong>
          </div>

          <div class="building-row">
            <span>Technical</span>
            <strong>2</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>

  </section>

</main>

<footer>
  © 2026 Gemeinde Sonnenfeld. Notifications updated: 15 Jan 2026, 09:15 CET.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
